            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>Government Records held at the National Archives, with certain exceptions, become
                    public after a 30 year closure period.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>National Archives: Government Headquarters, Church Street, Basseterre, St.
                    Kitts.</p>
                <p> Ministry of Foreign Affairs: P. O. Box 186, Church Street, Basseterre, St. Kitts
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Members of the public may access the research room and finding aids after
                    registering with the Archives.</p>
